It's a quilt.

235
00:24:47,520 --> 00:24:48,180
Move aside.

236
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:56,120
It's completely pointless.

237
00:24:56,560 --> 00:24:59,120
This is typical childish drama, just playing house.

238
00:24:59,120 --> 00:25:01,360
Life has its ups and downs, that's inevitable.

239
00:25:01,360 --> 00:25:03,160
Crying over every little thing,

240
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:04,960
you can't just cry your way back to the womb,

241
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:06,320
how will you ever grow up?

242
00:25:06,320 --> 00:25:08,120
You're all like the morning sun,

243
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:10,120
just starting to shine,

244
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:12,460
and acting like it's the end of the world.

245
00:25:14,120 --> 00:25:15,650
What a dangerous day it was!

246
00:25:15,680 --> 00:25:16,560
Three lives

247
00:25:16,880 --> 00:25:18,560
