275
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:06,000
You're used to interrupting, aren't you?

276
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:07,260
The director is right,

277
00:26:07,320 --> 00:26:08,440
turn grief into strength.

278
00:26:08,440 --> 00:26:09,770
Fold up those blankets,

279
00:26:09,960 --> 00:26:12,220
you're all sitting there like grandmas.

280
00:26:12,360 --> 00:26:13,320
I'm naked.

281
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:14,960
Get dressed.

282
00:26:23,840 --> 00:26:26,360
