283
00:26:26,360 --> 00:26:27,160
I'm cold.

284
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:27,840
It's wet.

285
00:26:28,080 --> 00:26:28,720
Go, go,

286
00:26:28,720 --> 00:26:29,780
go change quickly.

287
00:26:32,520 --> 00:26:33,120
Xiaoyao,

288
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:34,940
is there any hot water?

289
00:26:36,120 --> 00:26:37,450
There's a water heater.

290
00:26:41,160 --> 00:26:42,160
You're all so good

291
00:26:42,320 --> 00:26:43,480
at fooling me.

292
00:26:44,800 --> 00:26:46,520
